reviews.review_text:
Pretty awful I’ll start with the good aspects of the show…….

The Grateful Dead played a show at the Orpheum in San Francisco on 7/1/13/76 and were able to start and finish songs.

What else? The mix is good

“High Time” indeed.

And I thought the dark days of the 80s and 90s were bad. Obviously, I was wrong.

You have been warned.
